org.hps.record.daqconfig2019

Class VTPConfig2019

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.daqconfig2019.IDAQConfig2019
      • org.hps.record.daqconfig2019.VTPConfig2019

  • public class VTPConfig2019
extends IDAQConfig2019
    Class VTPConfig2019 stores VTP configuration settings parsed from the an EVIO file. This class manages the following properties:
    • Singles 1 Trigger
    • Singles 2 Trigger
    • Singles 3 Trigger
    • Singles 4 Trigger
    • Pair 1 Trigger
    • Pair 2 Trigger
    • Pair 3 Trigger
    • Pair 4 Trigger
